profile:
Mr. Sandless of Kelowna B.C. is a full service floor refinishing and installation company. We offer our patented no sanding and dustless sanding solutions that will have your wooden floors looking beautiful for about half the cost of traditional sanding,

 
The process is certified green, is kid and pet safe, and the non-toxic finishes leave no odour! Most jobs can be finished in one day!They service the entire Okanagan valley and surrounding areas.

 
The #1 brand of wood refinishing in the world, guaranteed not to crack, chip, peel or yellow with their five year warranty! Mr. Sandless refinishes all types of hardwood, engineered wood, veneer, laminates, VCT, ceramic tile, Linoleum, terrazzo, concrete and more! They can do floor, cabinets, bar tops and tables, etc.
